snippet.title: Amber Heard & Friends: Constant Contradictions! With Friends Like These...
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #metoo

Hey everyone! Welcome back!  This video is my take, my break, my analysis of the recent story of a second (mystery) 911 call about the abuse allegations made by Amber Heard against Johnny Depp.

I also present new evidence, testimony, and shocking new revelations concerning Amber's friends!

Thanks for watching, sharing, commenting, and reaching out here and on other platforms.  Take care!

Instagram: @IncrediblyAverageBrian
Twitter: @ThatBrianFella
